  {
    "title": "Story",
    "depth": 0,
    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "\"Genius ninja in the Shadow Sect who is at the crossroads\""
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "A genius ninja of the Shadow Sect in the Scarlet Shadow."
          },
          {
            "text": "In order to pursue great power, he absorbed the \"Hanekage\" into his body, and used the enemy's flesh and blood to provide nourishment for the \"Hanekage\"."
          },
          {
            "text": "After gaining power, he took away the most powerful supreme ninjutsu and Ame no Habakiri in the Scarlet Shadow, and went further and further on the road of killing."
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
