  {
    "title": "The End of Nindo",
    "depth": 1,
    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "\"To protect the secrets of the Sacred Tools is your duty; value it more than your life.\""
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "As Hanzo awoke in the middle of the night due to pain inflicted by the Ame no Habakiri, he recalled this teaching that led him down this path of no return."
          },
          {
            "text": "Before turning his back on the Scarlet Shadow, Hanzo was the Shadow Sect's sharpest blade."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Adopted by the Shadow Sect at a young age, Hanzo was lucky to escape the fate of a wandering beggar."
          },
          {
            "text": "He learned the ways of Nindo, to \"uphold justice and endure hardship\", and lived his new life by its teachings."
          },
          {
            "text": "For the Scarlet Shadow, his cherished home, he was willing to do anything."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Fierce and tenacious like the wolf, Hanzo always took on the most perilous missions."
          },
          {
            "text": "Even when he returned with grave injuries, he would make his report in full before seeking treatment."
          },
          {
            "text": "Failure was something not even Hanzo's greatest rivals would dare think of."
          },
          {
            "text": "They knew Hanzo would stop at nothing to achieve his objectives."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Over the course of a decade, Hanzo accumulated so many merits that his peers saw him, a commoner by birth, as only second to Kurēn, the clan's next heir."
          },
          {
            "text": "Hanzo acknowledged Kurēn's unmatched wisdom."
          },
          {
            "text": "If Kurēn vowed to uphold Nindo after he took power, then Hanzo would become his sharpest blade."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Until now, Hanzo never thought his past self was wrong, but it was his near-obsessive persistence that led him to this point."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Some time ago, Hanzo, while engrossed in the Nindo scriptures, suddenly realized that his peers, other orphans adopted by the clan, had routinely disappeared with little explanation."
          },
          {
            "text": "Greatly puzzled, Hanzo began to investigate on his own."
          },
          {
            "text": "During his search, he crossed more than a few elders, resulting in him being stripped of all rank in the clan."
          },
          {
            "text": "The merits he earned at the risk of his life were erased overnight."
          },
          {
            "text": "Hanzo cared little for fame, but he knew something sinister was being covered up."
          },
          {
            "text": "Eventually, he discovered that the elders had been sending ninjas on missions to the forbidden grounds to steal a Cursed Tool that was supposed to be sealed within: the demonic blade Ame no Habakiri."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Countless lives had been sacrificed to the demon blade."
          },
          {
            "text": "Hanzo couldn't bear to think how many in the Scarlet Shadow who simply sought to uphold justice ended up with this fate."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "A momentary lapse in concentration caused Hanzo to be discovered by another ninja in the forbidden grounds―it was Kurēn."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "In the dark, stone chamber, Kurēn revealed the truth of the Scarlet Shadow: The two factions within the clan had been vying for control of the Seven Sacred Tools, each trying to shift the balance of power in their favor."
          },
          {
            "text": "The elders of the Shadow Sect were sacrificing their own to the Ame no Habakiri in order to awaken its true power."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Kurēn had been secretly gaining influence to abolish this vile practice once he became the clan leader, and seeing Hanzo, he was eager to have a ninja of Nindo help him change the future of the clan."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "\"Those that were sacrificed to Ame no Habakiri... what of their futures?\""
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Kurēn had no answer to his question, which sent Hanzo into a rage."
          },
          {
            "text": "He had seen too many hypocrites claiming to act for the greater good, and in that moment, he realized the Scarlet Shadow was no different."
          },
          {
            "text": "His Nindo did not tolerate evil deeds, thus the Scarlet Shadow should not exist."
          },
          {
            "text": "If they craved Ame no Habakiri's power so much, he would show them its true might"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "As Hanzo reached for the demon blade on the pedestal, he thought to himself, \"Come, either devour me, or let me devour everything!\""
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "The moment he grasped the Ame no Habakiri, its unbridled demonic power invaded his body."
          },
          {
            "text": "In a trance, he saw a whirlpool swallowing ships, or was it a leviathan devouring entire islands?"
          },
          {
            "text": "Quickly he realized what he was actually seeing:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "It was a vortex of souls; the ninjas who had been sacrificed, and countless more before them."
          },
          {
            "text": "Their wills had long been erased, leaving only an insatiable hunger and darkness churning within the blade; a madness that was neither human nor demon."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "The demonic power invaded Hanzo's very being, but his pride refused to be consumed."
          },
          {
            "text": "Feeding on his rage and obsession, he finally tamed the Ame no Habakiri."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "\"Naive pretender, you will witness my reign from within this blade.\""
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "And with that, Hanzo swung the blade at his former comrade Kurēn."
          },
          {
            "text": "\"Gaining influence\"... that's merely the cowardly compromise of the weak."
          },
          {
            "text": "Without the courage to make the first cut, there would never be change."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "After devouring Kurēn, Hanzo left the forbidden grounds."
          },
          {
            "text": "He knew his path as a ninja of the Shadow Sect ninja was forever severed."
          },
          {
            "text": "But what of it?########[p]This Akuma shall carve out the rot from within the Scarlet Shadow once and for all."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
